timing_contex..._clock_mapping(25.10)    timing_contex..._clock_mapping(25.10)

Name
       timing_context_data_phase_based_clock_mapping

Syntax
       timing_context_data_phase_based_clock_mapping

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set  to  true, the port-based clock mapping search is enhanced by
       additionally trying to map originally unmapped top clocks.

       Such unmapped top clock on data port is to be mapped to block clock  if
       top clock was mapped to block clock on other data ports.

       Note:    This    variable    can    be    applied    when   timing_con-
       text_port_based_clock_mapping is set to true.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

